Prompt Template for AI
"I need a toggle-controlled drawer animation that:

Trigger: A boolean variable (e.g., LAUNCHER_OPEN) that toggles on button click
Animation Type: Revealer with slideright transition — smooth spring-like entrance from left edge
Duration: 300-400ms with ease-out-cubic easing for a "bouncy" feel
Content: A vertical box containing quick launcher buttons/icons
Behavior:
When toggled true → drawer slides in from left, revealing launcher buttons
When toggled false → drawer slides left, hiding launcher buttons
No animation when window is closed (idle efficiency)
Visual description: Think of it like a spring-loaded sidebar that smoothly unfolds from the left edge with a pleasant deceleration curve, not jerky or robotic."

