Technical Breakdown (For Code Generation)
Code
Animation Properties:
├─ Widget Type: revealer
├─ Direction: slideright (left → right = drawer appearing)
├─ Duration: 300ms (or 350ms for more spring-like)
├─ Easing: ease-out-cubic 
│  (fast start, smooth deceleration = spring feel)
├─ Trigger: toggle variable (true/false)
├─ State: reveal-child = LAUNCHER_VISIBLE
└─ Container: vertical box with launcher items

Interaction Flow:
1. User clicks toggle button
2. LAUNCHER_VISIBLE flips (false → true or true → false)
3. Revealer detects state change
4. Animation plays: 300ms slideright with ease-out-cubic
5. Drawers slides in/out smoothly
