Why These Terms Work
"slideright" → AI knows this is a GTK4 revealer transition
"ease-out-cubic" → Specific easing function (not generic "smooth")
"300ms" → Concrete timing (feels responsive, not slow)
"spring-like" → Conveys the feel/aesthetic you want
"toggle variable" → AI understands reactive state binding
"drawer from left" → Clear directional intent

